λά[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></span>  <br id=\"al13-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κόϊντος ήσις ωτιανός\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Κόϊντος\">Κ(όϊντος?)</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"ήσις\">[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.</span>]ήσις</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"ωτιανός\">[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ω̣τιανός</span></span>  <br id=\"al14-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γάϊος ιφκρατος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Γάϊος\">Γ(άϊος)</span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ιφ̣[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]κ̣ρατος</span>  <br id=\"al15-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">15</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γάϊος μητος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenoman\" data-text=\"Γάϊος\">Γ(άϊος)</span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]μητος</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. ..ΟΛΩΝΙἈπόλωνι</p>"
    },
